              You get to choose the best technologies that work for your projects. You are not tied to specific languages, platforms, or services. We are free to tinker and experiment as we see fit. 
            

              Omar, Software Engineer
            

Meet Omar. A Master's-level graduate of the University of Michigan, he enjoys the collaborative nature of his team where finding creative solutions to problems is always a group effort. 


















              DRW is genuinely a meritocracy. As a firm, we reward new ideas and divergent thinking. I’ve seen it firsthand, and it is one of the reasons why I enjoy working here.
            

              Amit, Head of Fixed Income Analytics 
            

Meet Amit. A graduate of Stanford University, he is a former trader who now focuses on building analytical tools and testing new trading strategies. 


















              There are no big egos and people are willing to consider out-of-the-box solutions. 
            

              Kumbi, Senior Network Engineer
            

Meet Kumbi. A CCIE and network expert who hails from Zimbabwe, DRW has offered him an opportunity to improve his project delivery skills on a global basis, having worked with teams around the world. 


















               I came to DRW straight out of college with no background in finance.  Since then, I’ve been learning nonstop.
            

